snippet.title: Snow Drift (Nitrome.com) - Full Gameplay Levels 1-20
snippet.description:
Full gameplay of Snow Drift.
A Nitrome game from 2007 about a yeti that hates penguins and can't drift in snow, just in ice.
I hope you like it!
